ASoC: SOF: Intel: hda: Simplify the hda_dsp_wait_d0i3c_done() function

Remove the retry argument for the hda_dsp_wait_d0i3c_done()
function and use the HDA_DSP_REG_POLL_RETRY_COUNT macro
directly.

